</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_389" id="193v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Johannsen, bischof zu Wirczburg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><app>
<note place="marginleft">+</note>
</app>
<expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ewr gnade
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> und kawfflewt und auch ir habe und
                                <expan>kawffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan> und die iren in die
                                <expan>nehstkünftig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Frankfurt<ex>er</ex></expan> vastenmesse und
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> darawsz mit geleyt
                                <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> fürsehen welle; also ob sie
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> die iren zu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> oder <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und des <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz
                        denn sie und das ir durch <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> lande, <expan>h<ex>e</ex>rschaft</expan> und
                        gepiete sicher geleytet <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, als etc. Das wellen
                        etc. Und bitten des ewr gnedig <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> bey disem
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab></div>
<div type="similiter"><pb facs="#facs_390" id="194r"/><ab>+ Graf Johannsen von Wertheim<lb/> + <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lienhart<ex>en</ex></expan>, grafen und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu Castell<lb/>
<expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> Schenken, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                        Lyntpurg<lb/> + <expan>Arnolt<ex>en</ex></expan> von Sekendorff,
                                <expan>amptm<ex>an</ex></expan> zu der Newenstat an der Eysch<lb/> +
                                <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                            <expan>burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                        <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan><lb/> + Dem edeln
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wilhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> von Rechberg von
                                <expan>Hohenrechb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>amptm</expan> zu Uffenheim<lb/>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> als dem
                            <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan>.<lb/> + <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu
                        Hohenloch <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> doch durch des von
                        Weinsperg lande und gepiet, des gewalt er in den
                            <expan>dinge<ex>n</ex></expan> habe, als wir
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> haben.<lb/>Graf Thomas von Ryeneck<app>
<note place="bottomcentral">
<expan>No<ex>ta</ex></expan> allen
                                    <expan>officialib<ex>us</ex></expan> et sic mutiern, wenn sie
                                        <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> die iren
                                    <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu ewch
                                    <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und des
                                    <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, daz ir denn sie und das ir durch
                                die gepiete, <expan>alsv<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ir zu
                                    <add>geleyten</add> habt, <expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan>
                                geleyten wellet. Als etc. </note>
</app></ab></div>
</div></body>
